using: div and span for Albert's_Blog;
      'Button and icons for buttons;'
       className 'for padding bording(px-horizontal, px-vertical);'
       whitespace-nowrap: 'dont move to new string'
      font-semibold dark:text-white "midle girnost texta & beliy text na temnoy teme'
       Navbar.Toggle - menu after Sign In button when became sm screen"
       
       useLocation(need import)-'for active devinetly styles and components
                                 depends on path'
       BUT: <Navbar.Link active={path === '/'}>
           <Link to="/">Home</Link>
      make error: validateDOMNesting(...): <a> cannot appear as a descendant of <a>.
      cause 2 links SO NEED do like:
            <Navbar.Link active={path === '/'} as={'div'}>
           <Link to="/">Home</Link>

